{
  "uid": "tip-consensus-health",
  "title": "TIP Consensus Health",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "tags": [
    "tip",
    "consensus",
    "health"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "node",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prom-tip"
        },
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(tip_node_registry_info, node)",
          "refId": "vars"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Action needed?  (green = healthy, red = investigate)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Halted nodes",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Nodes whose consensus halt-gate is tripped (stale rounds / sub-quorum / fork).\n\nNormal: 0.\nAct if: >0 sustained, a node has stopped finalizing.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(tip_consensus_halted == 1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "0 HEALTHY"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Consensus divergence (byzantine-fork canary)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 1,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 3
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(tip_consensus_divergence_total)",
          "legendFormat": "total"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 14,
          "valueSize": 26
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "description": "**Consensus divergence** - Cumulative count of byzantine-fork events: anti-entropy saw two peers at the same `committed_round` but with different `state_merkle_root`.\n\n**Healthy**: 0. This counter SHOULD never tick. It's a canary, not a liveness signal.\n\n**Trouble**: any value > 0 means two nodes have diverged on canonical state at the same round. This is a critical safety event - page immediately. Do NOT auto-resolve. Investigate which fork is correct, halt the wrong one."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Nodes online",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Nodes whose /metrics responded to the last scrape.\n\nNormal: 5.\nAct if: <4 (below quorum), a node's thread is blocked or it crashed.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 4
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 16,
        "y": 1,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Quorum margin (min)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Smallest (active participants minus quorum) across the federation.\n\nNormal: >=1.\nAct if: 0, the federation is at the edge; any single drop halts it.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "min(tip_consensus_quorum_margin)",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Quorum threshold",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 3
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max(tip_narwhal_quorum and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1))"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "description": "**Quorum threshold** - The 2f+1 majority needed for Bullshark to commit an anchor, derived from the active committee size. For N nodes: quorum = floor(2N/3) + 1.\n\n**Healthy**: stable value matching the active committee.\n\n**Trouble**: changes unexpectedly = committee membership shifted (could be legitimate auto-derivation from `recent_producers` or a node being silently dropped)."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Worst event-loop stall",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Longest single event-loop block in the federation (last 1s window).\n\nNormal: <250ms.\nAct if: >1000ms sustained, the thread is starved; that node drops peers and goes offline.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max(tip_process_event_loop_lag_max_ms)",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 250
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1000
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 14,
        "y": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Suspect peers",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Peers any node currently can't reach via heartbeat.\n\nNormal: 0.\nAct if: >0 sustained, each suspect triggers an anti-entropy sync storm (the jitter feedback loop).",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(tip_heartbeat_suspect_peers) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "0 CALM"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Commit rate",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Anchors committed per minute across the federation.\n\nNormal: >0 (advancing).\nAct if: 0, consensus is not finalizing anything.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(tip_bullshark_anchors_committed_total[2m])) * 60 or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cpm",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.5
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "textMode": "value",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Consensus progress",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 13,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Committed round per node",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "The last round each node finalized.\n\nNormal: all lines rise together, tightly bunched.\nAct if: a line flatlines (that node stalled) or sits far below the others (sync gap).",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(tip_bullshark_last_committed_round{node=~\"$node\"} * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info)))",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 11
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Commit spread: leader minus laggard",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "How many rounds the most-behind node trails the leader.\n\nNormal: <5.\nAct if: >20 sustained, a node is falling behind and anti-entropy isn't closing the gap.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max(tip_bullshark_last_committed_round) - min(tip_bullshark_last_committed_round)",
          "legendFormat": "spread (rounds)"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 5
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 20
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 11
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Consensus index (anchor commits since genesis) - per node",
      "description": "**Consensus index** - Network-wide count of anchor commits. Persisted via `consensus_meta` (#44) so it survives restart on idle networks; joining nodes adopt the cluster's value at snapshot install time via `peer_consensus_index` (Cosmos/Sui pattern), so all caught-up nodes converge to the same value.\n\n**Healthy**: all online nodes report the same value (modulo 1-2 of in-flight drift), monotonically increasing.\n\n**Trouble**: a node's value frozen for > 3 minutes = consensus halted on that node. Sustained large absolute-value drift between nodes = a joiner didn't pick up snapshot-based convergence; check sync logs.\n\nFor commit rate, see the next panel (Consensus advance rate) - it's sourced from a per-process counter that's immune to snapshot-adoption jumps. Alert: `rate(tip_bullshark_anchors_committed_total[5m]) == 0 for: 3m`.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "((tip_bullshark_consensus_index{node=~\"$node\"} * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info)))) and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "displayMode": "lcd",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 13,
          "valueSize": 16
        },
        "valueMode": "color",
        "namePlacement": "left",
        "minVizWidth": 0,
        "minVizHeight": 22,
        "sizing": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "max": null,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Consensus advance rate (anchors/min) - per node",
      "description": "**Consensus advance rate (anchors/min)** - Rate at which Bullshark commits anchor certs, per minute, over a 5-minute window. Sourced from `tip_bullshark_anchors_committed_total` - a per-process counter that ticks only on real local anchor commits.\n\n**Why not `rate(consensus_index)`?** `consensus_index` jumps when a joining node adopts the peer's network-wide value via `peer_consensus_index` (snapshot fast-sync). That one-step jump produces a spurious rate spike for ~5 min after each new joiner. The per-process anchor counter is immune to those jumps.\n\n**Healthy**: ~25-30 anchors/min on every node, all within ~1/min of each other (Bullshark commits at ~2s cadence).\n\n**Trouble**:\n- Any node < 1/min for 3+ min = consensus halted on that node\n- One node consistently lower than others = lagging, AE should auto-recover\n- All nodes drop together = federation-wide halt (check halt-status panel)\n\nAlertmanager: `rate(tip_bullshark_anchors_committed_total[5m]) == 0 for: 3m`.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 25,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "((rate(tip_bullshark_anchors_committed_total{node=~\"$node\"}[5m]) * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info))) * 60) and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "displayMode": "lcd",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "text": {
          "titleSize": 13,
          "valueSize": 16
        },
        "valueMode": "color",
        "namePlacement": "left",
        "minVizWidth": 0,
        "minVizHeight": 22,
        "sizing": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "max": 35,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Narwhal current round",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 31,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "((tip_narwhal_current_round{node=~\"$node\"} * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info)))) and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "description": "**Narwhal current round** - The round Narwhal is currently producing batches at. Always 1-2 rounds ahead of `last_committed_round` since Bullshark needs the next wave's votes before finalizing.\n\n**Healthy**: linear monotonic growth on all nodes; convergent across the federation.\n\n**Trouble**: flat line on any node = production stalled (likely halt-gate); large drift between nodes = sync gap that anti-entropy should auto-recover (#28/#46)."
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Bullshark commits / 5s",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 31,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(rate(tip_bullshark_anchors_committed_total{node=~\"$node\"}[1m]) * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info))) and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max"
          ]
        }
      },
      "description": "**Bullshark commits / 5s** - Rate of anchor commits in 5-second windows.\n\n**Healthy**: ~2-3 commits per 5s on a 2-second-round network. All nodes show the same rate.\n\n**Trouble**: zero or sporadic - consensus is failing to make progress (check halt status + peer connectivity)."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Quorum, jitter & certs",
