            "mean"
          ]
        }
      },
      "description": "**Cert GC (rounds pruned)** - Cumulative count of certificate rows pruned by Bullshark's GC trigger (every `gc_interval_commits`, prunes certs older than `gc_depth` rounds).\n\n**Healthy**: linearly growing, lagging the anchor commit rate by gc_depth rounds.\n\n**Trouble**: stuck at 0 with high commit count = GC isn't firing (check `TIP_GC_DISABLED` env). Sudden huge jump = lots of certs pruned at once (after a long offline period)."
    },
