    {
      "id": 29,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Mempool throughput (submit / drain rate)",
      "description": "**Mempool throughput** - Cumulative-counter rate of txs entering and leaving the mempool, per second.\n\n- **received**: `rate(tip_mempool_received_total[1m])` - submit rate (txs accepted into the mempool)\n- **drained**: `rate(tip_mempool_drained_total[1m])` - commit rate (txs pulled into Narwhal batches)\n\n**Healthy**: drained tracks received closely on a busy network. On idle, both stay flat at 0.\n\n**Trouble**:\n- received > drained sustained = consensus can't keep up; mempool grows unbounded (see Mempool size over time)\n- received > 0 with drained = 0 = halt-gate is engaged or batches aren't being pulled (#26/#27)\n- drained > received = catching up on backlog (transient, healthy)\n\nThese counters fix the sampling blind spot of the gauge: gauge can return to 0 between scrapes; counters never miss transient flow.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 100,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(rate(tip_mempool_received_total{node=~\"$node\"}[1m]) * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info))) and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} received"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "(rate(tip_mempool_drained_total{node=~\"$node\"}[1m]) * on(node) group_left(name) (group by (node, name) (tip_node_registry_info))) and on(instance) (up{job=\"tip-federation\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} drained"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
